text:
@TMobile next time you send me my new device don't use @UPS for sending it, shit courier service even with your 2nd day air shipping. Was supposed to get my package on 21st, won't be getting it until 25th.

No Thanks!
@UPSHelp You guys have the worst customer service. Sent an email 2 days ago didn't even get a response.

Now they email me saying the package will be held at a location 30 minutes away from me, when there is a UPS Access point right next door.

You guys aren't doing yourself any favors by making it difficult for me to get a single package. @UPSHelp

@sidharathc I can see you are upset, and understandably so! Please DM the details to my team, so we can review the situation further. I'd like to see what can be done to help resolve the matter. Please also provide the tracking number, address, and your contact phone number. ^WS
